{"id":80,"name":"عبس","transliteration":"'Abasa","translation":"皱眉","type":"meccan","total_verses":42,"verses":[{"id":1,"text":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","translation":"他曾皱眉，而且转身离去，","transliteration":"AAabasa watawalla"},{"id":2,"text":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","translation":"因为那个盲人来到他的面前。","transliteration":"An jaahu alaAAma"},{"id":3,"text":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","translation":"你怎能知道呢？他也许能受熏陶，","transliteration":"Wama yudreeka laAAallahu yazzakka"},{"id":4,"text":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","translation":"或听忠告，而蒙教益。","transliteration":"Aw yaththakkaru fatanfaAAahu alththikra"},{"id":5,"text":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","translation":"至于自满者，","transliteration":"Amma mani istaghna"},{"id":6,"text":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","translation":"你都逢迎他，","transliteration":"Faanta lahu tasadda"},{"id":7,"text":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","translation":"他不受熏陶，于你何干？","transliteration":"Wama AAalayka alla yazzakka"},{"id":8,"text":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","translation":"至于殷勤地来请教你，","transliteration":"Waamma man jaaka yasAAa"},{"id":9,"text":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","translation":"而且心怀敬畏者，","transliteration":"Wahuwa yakhsha"},{"id":10,"text":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","translation":"你却怠慢他。","transliteration":"Faanta AAanhu talahha"},{"id":11,"text":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","translation":"绝不然！这确是一种教训。","transliteration":"Kalla innaha tathkiratun"},{"id":12,"text":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","translation":"谁欲诵读它，就叫谁诵读它吧","transliteration":"Faman shaa thakarahu"},{"id":13,"text":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","translation":"它在珍贵的册页里；","transliteration":"Fee suhufin mukarramatin"},{"id":14,"text":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","translation":"那些册页，是被称扬的，是被涤净的，","transliteration":"MarfooAAatin mutahharatin"},{"id":15,"text":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","translation":"是在许多书记的手里的；","transliteration":"Biaydee safaratin"},{"id":16,"text":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","translation":"那些书记，是尊贵的，是善良的。","transliteration":"Kiramin bararatin"},{"id":17,"text":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","translation":"该死的人！他是何等的忘恩！","transliteration":"Qutila alinsanu ma akfarahu"},{"id":18,"text":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","translation":"安拉曾用什么创造他的呢？","transliteration":"Min ayyi shayin khalaqahu"},{"id":19,"text":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","translation":"是用精液。他曾创造他，并预定他发育的程序。","transliteration":"Min nutfatin khalaqahu faqaddarahu"},{"id":20,"text":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","translation":"然后，他使他的道路平易。","transliteration":"Thumma alssabeela yassarahu"},{"id":21,"text":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","translation":"然后，他使他死，并安葬他。","transliteration":"Thumma amatahu faaqbarahu"},{"id":22,"text":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","translation":"然后，当他意欲的时候，他使他复活。","transliteration":"Thumma itha shaa ansharahu"},{"id":23,"text":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","translation":"绝不然，他还没有奉行他所命令他的事务。","transliteration":"Kalla lamma yaqdi ma amarahu"},{"id":24,"text":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","translation":"教人观察自己的食物吧！","transliteration":"Falyanthuri alinsanu ila taAAamihi"},{"id":25,"text":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","translation":"我将雨水大量地倾注下来。","transliteration":"Anna sababna almaa sabban"},{"id":26,"text":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","translation":"然后，我使地面奇异地裂开，","transliteration":"Thumma shaqaqna alarda shaqqan"},{"id":27,"text":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","translation":"我在大地上生产百谷，","transliteration":"Faanbatna feeha habban"},{"id":28,"text":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","translation":"与葡萄和苜蓿，","transliteration":"WaAAinaban waqadban"},{"id":29,"text":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","translation":"与橄榄和海枣，","transliteration":"Wazaytoonan wanakhlan"},{"id":30,"text":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","translation":"与茂密的园圃，","transliteration":"Wahadaiqa ghulban"},{"id":31,"text":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","translation":"水果和牧草，","transliteration":"Wafakihatan waabban"},{"id":32,"text":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","translation":"以供你们和你们的牲畜享受。","transliteration":"MataAAan lakum walianAAamikum"},{"id":33,"text":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","translation":"当震耳欲聋的轰声来临的时候，","transliteration":"Faitha jaati alssakhkhatu"},{"id":34,"text":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","translation":"在那日，各人将逃避自己的弟兄、","transliteration":"Yawma yafirru almaro min akheehi"},{"id":35,"text":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","translation":"自己的父母、","transliteration":"Waommihi waabeehi"},{"id":36,"text":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","translation":"自己的妻子儿女；","transliteration":"Wasahibatihi wabaneehi"},{"id":37,"text":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","translation":"在那日，各人将自顾不暇；","transliteration":"Likulli imriin minhum yawmaithin shanun yughneehi"},{"id":38,"text":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","translation":"在那日，许多面目是光华的，","transliteration":"Wujoohun yawmaithin musfiratun"},{"id":39,"text":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","translation":"是喜笑的，是愉快的；","transliteration":"Dahikatun mustabshiratun"},{"id":40,"text":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","translation":"在那日，许多面目上，将有灰尘，","transliteration":"Wawujoohun yawmaithin AAalayha ghabaratun"},{"id":41,"text":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","translation":"黧黑将蒙蔽它。","transliteration":"Tarhaquha qataratun"},{"id":42,"text":"أُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","translation":"这等人，是不信道的，是荒淫的。","transliteration":"Olaika humu alkafaratu alfajaratu"}]}
